					<div class="pdf24_01" style="left:14.9333em;top:9.9509em;"><span class="pdf24_07 pdf24_08 pdf24_11" style="word-spacing:0.0143em;">ATESTADO DE TREINAMENTO PARA ARRAIS-AMADOR &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="pdf24_01" style="left:7.3333em;top:12.3926em;"><span class="pdf24_12 pdf24_08 pdf24_13" style="word-spacing:0.0036em;">Campo de Preenchimento do Estabelecimento de Treinamento Náu</span><span class="pdf24_14 pdf24_08 pdf24_15">t</span><span class="pdf24_12 pdf24_08 pdf24_16">co &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="pdf24_01" style="left:7.7792em;top:14.1676em;"><span class="pdf24_12 pdf24_08 pdf24_17" style="word-spacing:0.005em;">Atesto, para os devidos ﬁns, que o(a) Sr.(a.) &nbsp;</span></div>
